shortcode_media.title: Lockdown Diaries: Entry Eleven, Eda’s Life in Lockdown

node.text: Song- Best Day Of My Life @americanauthors

Eda shared her experience of the lockdown with us from London.

In the past months we had been subjected to strict quarantine measures to slow the flow of the virus in society, and most people are now more conscious of minimalism as a result. Many are realising that what we have more of than we really need and less is more. 

Thanks for watching hope you enjoyed this fun chat we had with Eda. 

Stay safe x

node.text:
eBOOK LAUNCH
.
This day has finally arrived!! ??
I’m elated to announce the launch of my new ebook ‘In The Kitchen With Paz’ Cookbook, available on the Amazon website. I hope you indulge in the recipes and it brings a warm delight when you recreate my kitchen into your home. You’ll find the link in the profile. 
.
In frame: A classic combination of garlic, lemon juice and authentic spices in an easy one-pan week night dinner of ‘Nandos -Inspired Chicken’ with the secret resting squarely in the sauce.
.
A formidable sauce basks in the combination of bold spices, developing into a mildly warming heat, which can easily be tailored, to suit your taste buds. 

A creamy and buttery sauce with an irresistible garlicky flavor and just a mild tang from the fresh lemon juice, this sauce clings with intent. Best served with roughly torn naan for indulgent sauce mopping. Recipe available in my new ebook.

Follow @foodiesof_cakewalk for more photos and ideas/recipes. Tag me should you recreate any of my foods, I’d love to share them. .

node.text:
Zucchini Rolattini

Whenever we think of Italian food the mind pops up with Pizzas, pastas, lasagnas loaded with cheese and not very healthy option 'All purpose flour'.. 
So thought of giving it some healthy twist by using thin ribbons of zucchini, wrapped it around cottage cheese and spinach filling, sprinkled some mozzarella cheese and baked it on the bed of homemade Marinara sauce.. ? 
The result was scrumptious. A healthy alternative to satiate your Italian cravings?

Sending this as my initiative to #glutenfreewithmeena hosted by @theredplatechronicles
Sponsored by @indian__natives @justafarmer.in 
Featured by @yesindia 

I further nominate @niks_ash @komalagarrwal @kantisingh82 to participate in it....
